title: For Sale/Trade:  model of 1903/30  turkish mauser
postcontent: The 1903 is a large ring 1898 style Mauser but with a 1893 style small shank Barrel according to Olson 200000 of these were made in oberndorf between 1903 and 1905. When these were converted from their original 7.65 millimeter to 7.92 millimeter , the receiver was slightly notched to easily allow loading of the slightly longer round. The bolt and magazine of the 1903 is also shorter than an actual 8mm model 98. This is an intermediate action and the bolt and magazine are 0.2 inches shorter than a standard length 98 action. The receiver face is coincidentally 0.2 longer than a 98. Other intermediates include the M24 the Yugoslavian models 4748 and several South American contract rifles.reply by call or text is best REDACTEDRifle gets excellent 2 inch groups at 100 yards.MIL surp.

title: For Sale:  CZ Scorpion EVO 3 S1 Carbine w/ Faux Suppressor
postcontent: Available in two variants, the Scorpion Carbine is a whole new animal. Building on the lauded submachinegun platform that first hit the US civilian market in pistol form in 2015, the Carbine has a 16.2? barrel fitted with either a compensating muzzle brake or a faux suppressor built specifically for CZ-USA by SilencerCo. Fit with the factory’s folding adjustable stock, the Carbine features a number of US-made parts to make it fully 922(r) compliant. One of the nicest features of the firearm is the newly-designed forend, covered in M-LOK attachment points to keep the profile slim while still being big enough to swallow most pistol-caliber suppressors should the owner decide down the road to convert it into an SBR for use with a suppressor. Low-profile aluminum adjustable sights round out the platform, and a top Picatinny rail allows the mounting of a wide number of optics. Simple and reliable, the Scorpion not only has ambidextrous controls, its non-reciprocating charging handle is swappable and reach to the trigger is adjustable. Carrying on the Scorpion’s reputation as a reliable pistol-caliber plinker without breaking the bank.
